{"route":{"route":"/posts/931c13a4/","outputPath":"posts/931c13a4/index.html","kind":"post","title":"GeoIP mmdb format","language":"en","params":{"abbrlink":"931c13a4"}},"description":"complete document MaxMind DB File Format SpecificationDescription here is only how convert trie tree to array trie array left is 0, right is 1 value is index of","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/GeoIP-mmdb-format.md","route":"/posts/931c13a4/","abbrlink":"931c13a4","title":"GeoIP mmdb format","date":"2020-07-27 22:15:17","updated":"2020-07-27 22:15:17","tags":["Network"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"en","htmlLang":"en","locale":"en_US","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"en-US","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","moreAnchor":"more","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>complete document <a href=\"https://maxmind.github.io/MaxMind-DB/\">MaxMind DB File Format SpecificationDescription</a></p>\n<p>here is only how convert trie tree to array</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-markdown\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">0100, 1011 -> trie</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">              root</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">               |</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">         +-----+------+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">        /              \\</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">       0                1</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">     /   \\             /  \\</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">   null   1           0   null</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">         / \\        /   \\</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">        0 null     null   1</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">       / \\               / \\</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">       0 null         null  1</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>trie -&gt; array<br>\nleft is 0, right is 1<br>\nvalue is index of array<span id=\"more\" class=\"post-more-anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-markdown\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> left | right  byte/index</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">2     |   4    0-1</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">null  |   6    2-3</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">8     |  null  4-5</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">10    |  null  6-7</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">null  |  12    8-9</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">14    |  null  10-11</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">null  |  16    11-12</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">end   |  null  12-13</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">null  |  end   13-14</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">array: [</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-light-text-decoration:underline;--shiki-dark:#DBEDFF;--shiki-dark-text-decoration:underline\">2,4,null,6,8,null,10,null,null,12,14,null,null,16,end,null,null,end</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">]</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>for example:</p>\n<p>index 1:<br>\nnext left index 2 is null, so 00* is not exist<br>\nnext right index 2+1 = 3 is not null, continue search until end or null</p>\n<p>this is one byte as one child, but one byte max is 255, if node more than 255, we can use multiple byte as one child</p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"931c13a4","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}